en_5274417_0	The ban on full face helmets will take effect from Thursday April 2.
en_5274417_1	Speaking to News1st Police Media Spokesperson ASP Ruwan Gunesekera said that the ban on full face helmets, which covers the face of the wearer, will be implemented from today.
en_5274417_2	He went onto note that the ban will not be strictly implemented at once.
en_5274417_3	ASP Gunesekera noted that they hope to gradually implement the laws.
